"title": "8723: doubt, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8723: doubt, results of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Doubt results in uncertainty and ineffectiveness in the spiritual life of individual believers and of the believing community. God appeals to those who waver to make a clear choice.</p>\n<h2>Doubt results in spiritual uncertainty</h2>\n<h3>Uncertainty about commitment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:57–9:62</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:19-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:19–8:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:17\">GEN 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:26\">GEN 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:2-Exod16:3\">EXO 16:2–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:15\">HEB 11:15</a></p>\n<h3>Uncertainty about God's power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:31\">NUM 13:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:29-Deut1:33\">DEU 1:29–1:33</a></p>\n<h3>Uncertainty about God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:27\">ISA 40:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:27\">DEU 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:16-Job9:18\">JOB 9:16–9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:21\">JOB 30:21</a></p>\n<h3>Uncertainty about the meaning of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:16\">JOB 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:3-Ps42:4\">PSA 42:3–42:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:14-Jer20:18\">JER 20:14–20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:3\">JON 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Uncertainty about teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20-1Tim6:21\">1TI 6:20–6:21</a></p>\n<h3>Uncertainty about the will of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:17\">JDG 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:36-Judg6:40\">JDG 6:36–6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:25\">JHN 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:3\">2CO 13:3</a></p>\n<h2>Doubt may result in a spiritual decline</h2>\n<h3>Doubt may result in drifting from faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1\">HEB 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:12-2Chr36:13\">2CH 36:12–36:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16-Neh9:17\">NEH 9:16–9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:8-Ps95:9\">PSA 95:8–95:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:20\">LAM 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:13\">HEB 3:12–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:20-2Pet2:21\">2PE 2:20–2:21</a></p>\n<h3>Doubt may result in faithless action</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">ISA 31:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:23\">ROM 14:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:13\">GEN 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:2-Gen16:3\">GEN 16:2–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:1\">EXO 32:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:11-Num20:12\">NUM 20:11–20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:40\">ACT 7:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:14\">ROM 14:14</a></p>\n<h3>Doubt brings the risk of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:12\">NUM 20:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1\">NUM 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:37\">NUM 14:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:7-Heb6:8\">HEB 6:7–6:8</a></p>\n<h2>Doubt leads to ineffectiveness in prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6-Jas1:7\">JAS 1:6–1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21\">MAT 21:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23\">MRK 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>Doubt spreads</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:28\">DEU 1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:32\">NUM 13:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14\">2KI 17:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's appeal for a clear decision</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:15-Deut30:17\">DEU 30:15–30:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:15\">JOS 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:27\">JHN 20:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a></p>",
